Gina 1.0.0
==========

    * Re-implemented from scratch in Vala
    * Add a menubar, which can be toggled on and off
    * Add the ability to turn off window decorations (not guaranteed to
      work with every window manager)
    * Use the GNU autotools for the build system


Gina 0.9.1
==========

    * Add checks on file type before opening
    * Remove the trailing newline if there is one
    * Rename functions to conform to the GTK+ naming conventions
    * Help window is now hidden when closed
    * Remove most of the ugly code
    * Improve Makefile


Gina 0.9.0
==========

    * First released version
    * 90% compatible with Nina 0.6.6
